# Charts Demo - Sparkline and BarChart with live data
# Shows animated charts for documentation

Output docs/recordings/components/charts.gif

Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 700
Set Height 280
Set Padding 20
Set PlaybackSpeed 1

# Hide setup
Hide
Type "pnpm tsx docs/component-demos/charts-demo.ts"
Enter
Sleep 800ms
Show

# Watch charts animate
Sleep 8s

Hide
Ctrl+C
